<cfmail to="#FORM.Email#" from="shari@sharis.com" subject="Thanks, #FORM.FirstName#!" >
Welcome #FORM.FirstName#,
	
We are honored that you have chosen to join Shari's Customer Community. Since opening our first restaurant over a quarter century ago, our goal has been to go beyond great food and friendly service, to build relationships with our customers. Long before email or the Internet, you could count on a smiling face and someone who knew your name every time you visited a Shari's Restaurant!

Now through the marvels of the computer, we're expanding the Shari's community beyond your local restaurant to the entire Shari's universe! Each month you will receive an email full of news and information from around the Shari's community, as well as introductions to our latest products, plus special offers available only to subscribers.

We always love to hear from you as well, because our goal is to provide the products and choices you're looking for when you choose a place for family dining. Feel free to email your comments and suggestions to customers@sharis.com. We look forward to hearing from you!

Eat well.
Sharis



